  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Peru Support Group - information and advocacy</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The PSG works to influence UK policy on Peru, provide reliable and updated information to a constituency in the UK and foster links between a wide range of CSOs, NGOs, and GOs in Peru and the UK. The PSG has chosen as its key themes: Political and economic analysis of current events and their impact on human rights; The social, economic and human rights impact of the Covid-19 pandemic; Business and human rights, energy transition, and extractive industries;  Climate change and its effect in Peru; The situation of women and other vulnerable groups, including LGBTI and indigenous people; The Right to Free, Prior and Informed Consent; Issues pertaining to rights to truth, justice and reparations.</narrative>
  </description>
